text:
Choco-senpai, the glasses looked adorable!
And in the photo, you looked so cool...!

Wow, thank you! As the model,
that's the best compliment I could get...!

Hey, how about checking out that glasses store's website?
Let's see what would suit Kaho!

Good job!
Hehe, I heard your energetic voice...

Ah, Natsuha-chan, good job!
We're going to have a glasses-finding session for Kaho now...
